quran[10{c,v,t}:
39,22,Afaman sharahal laahu sadrahoo lil Islaami fahuwa 'alaa noorim mir Rabbih; fa wailul lilqaasiyati quloobuhum min zikril laah; ulaaa'ika fee dalaalim mubeen
39,23,Allahu nazzala ahsanal hadeesi Kitaabam mutashaa biham masaaniy taqsha'irru minhu juloodul lazeena yakhshawna Rabbahum summa taleenu julooduhum wa quloo buhum ilaa zikril laah; zaalika hudal laahi yahdee bihee mai yashaaa'; wa mai yudlilil laahu famaa lahoo min haad
39,24,Afamai yattaqee biwaj hihee sooo'al 'azaabi Yawmal Qiyaamah; wa qeela lizzaali meena zooqoo maa kuntum taksiboon
39,25,Kazzabal lazeena min qablihim fa ataahumul 'azaabu min haisu laa yash'uroon
39,26,Fa azaaqahumul laahul khizya fil hayaatid dunyaa wa la'azaabul Aakirati akbar; law kaanoo ya'lamoon
39,27,Wa laqad darabnaa linnaasi fee haazal Qur-aani min kulli masalil la'allahum yatazakkaroon
39,28,Qur-aanan 'Arabiyyan ghaira zee 'iwajil la'allahum yattaqoon
39,29,Darabal laahu masalar rajulan feehi shurakaaa'u mutashaakisoona wa rajulan salamal lirajulin hal tastawi yaani masalaa; alhamdu lillaah; bal aksaruhum laa ya'lamoon
39,30,Innaka maiyitunw wa inna hum maiyitunw wa inna hum maiyitoon
39,31,Summa innakum Yawmal Qiyaamati 'inda Rabbikum takhtasimoon (section 3)�(End Juz 23)
